# 🚀 My Ansible Journey

Welcome to my Ansible learning and project repository!  
This repo documents my hands-on journey with **Ansible**, from basic playbooks to advanced automation for system administration, cloud, and DevOps workflows.  

---

## 📌 Goals of This Repository
- Learn and practice **Ansible fundamentals** (inventory, ad-hoc commands, playbooks).  
- Build reusable **roles** and **collections**.  
- Automate common tasks in **Linux administration** and **cloud environments** (Azure, AWS).  
- Share examples, experiments, and notes as I grow my skills.  

